Greetings,

We received a request to create an account for {{EMAIL}} on the {{CONFNAME}} submission site. If you made this request, please use this link to set a password:

{{PASSWORDLINK}}

If you did not make this request, it’s safe to ignore this email.

The link will work for 3 days. Should it expire, obtain a new link using "Forgot my password".

Contact {{ADMIN}} with any questions or concerns.

{{SIGNATURE}}
{{LINK}}

Greetings,

A system administrator has activated your {{EMAIL}} account on the {{CONFNAME}} submission site.

{{LINK}}

{{IF(NEEDPASSWORD)}}
You will need a password to sign in. Use this link to set one up:

{{PASSWORDLINK}}

Should the link expire, obtain a new one using "Forgot my password".
{{ENDIF}}

**NEW IN 2025**: Manage multiple accounts with different email addresses using Account settings > Manage email.

Contact {{ADMIN}} with any questions or concerns.

{{SIGNATURE}}
{{LINK}}

Greetings,

An account has been created for {{EMAIL}} on the {{CONFNAME}} submission site. You are now a contact for submission #{{PID}}. {{IF(ADMINUPDATE)}}An administrator performed this update.{{ENDIF}}

* Title: {{TITLE}}
* Author(s): {{OPT(AUTHORS)}}
* Site: {{LINK(paper, p={{PID}})}}

{{IF(NEEDPASSWORD)}}
You will need a password to sign in. Use this link to set one up:

{{PASSWORDLINK}}

Should the link expire, obtain a new one using "Forgot my password".
