Greetings,

{{CONFSHORTNAME}} submission #{{PID}}, which you reviewed or were assigned to review, has been withdrawn from consideration for the conference.

{{IF(ADMINUPDATE)}}
An administrator withdrew the submission. {{IF(REASON)}}They provided this reason: {{REASON}}{{ENDIF}}
{{ELSE}}
Authors can withdraw submissions during the review process. {{IF(REASON)}}They provided this reason: {{REASON}}{{ENDIF}}
